{"tid":320164,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[博狗會] 模擬賽馬投注平台 - 賽馬通勝 (2)","createTime":"2017-07-13T10:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T15:49:18.000Z","uid":66004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0df41c72af8e3886762ed247106aa7c26046e4e","tid":320164,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"話咁快又到季尾了，更新下近況先<br />\n<br />\n而家個app正式改左名叫: <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">賽馬通勝</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n總用戶數過左1萬了，平均一個賽馬日都有幾千個模擬投注<br />\n<br />\n最近亦開放左追蹤功能，不過我知道個功能未夠實用，所以大家個使用率都唔高。希望大家比下意見，講下有咩資訊應該加，我會趁休季改進。<br />\n<br />\n落飛燈個到唔好意思，而家要入多一頁先睇到，但我下個更新會改返好似之前咁的，個個會方便d<br />\n<br />\n呢期排行榜高手開始活躍起黎，個app即刻生猛曬。不過，d投注數據依然係顯示95%既人都係輸，得5%係有連續優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAnyway，歡迎大家討論下，因為我知道個平台仲有好多進步空間<br />\n<br />\n如果對足球通勝個即時比分功能有意見都可以講下，因為我係iOS加左，但唔知大家覺得好唔好用，所以仲未係Android到加，感謝<br />\n<br />\n上個post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/50272/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/50272/page/1</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dogeyclub.horseracingtracker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.dogeyclub.horseracingtracker&d=AUiwalGP1IppLLW2E0C4rDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8943c8fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dogeyclub.horseracingtracker</a><br />\niOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1173306897?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fid1173306897%3Fmt%3D8&d=AUiwalGP1IppLLW2E0C4rDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c1b53a89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1173306897?mt=8</a>"},{"pid":"91a06bf074eb41e3494777d338d6eba6056a86a9","tid":320164,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"仲有就係黎緊足球同賽馬都會加新既數據/統計資料，有冇咩資料係你特別想有既？"},{"pid":"eb06ac015d6c13511e5c4d97d4f6d0aeb8f5c1e6","tid":320164,"uid":26507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:40:46.000Z","msg":"可唔可以係馬名隔離整啲筆記位，例如係剔同交差咁？"},{"pid":"59906209d8c0679437a51e29b3f343bcea025fdf","tid":320164,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以係馬名隔離整啲筆記位，例如係剔同交差咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好提議wo，剔、交差同個人筆記都應該會有用<br />\n<br />\nthx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8781d377a5a016d98315548bb32a7458bc88c1e4","tid":320164,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:26:11.000Z","msg":"pushhh"},{"pid":"5b20bd2056c08151cc00d7aac5069376f143455f","tid":320164,"uid":71502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03692ea3c8e0251a7300766135e1c37578871077","tid":320164,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打覺得唔好用嗎？不妨講下意見呀"},{"pid":"81120febcbdbd7d3df943a20bd8d9a677e877fef","tid":320164,"uid":3611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ce1eedec6a431e3bd6a0a2085e9f986a70d2613","tid":320164,"uid":125931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"留名下先"},{"pid":"1158b1c3e47bd4a95131b15d44f8fb65cdf7f520","tid":320164,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>足球通勝有冇機會做到走地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一開始係有的，但因為需要好多資源去保持公正性同穩定性，所以無幾耐就取消左"}]}